        "description": "Get all images in an account.<br><br>*Rate limits*:<br>Burst: `10/s`<br>Steady: `150/m`\n\n**Scopes:**\n`images:read`\n\n[OpenAPI Spec](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/klaviyo/openapi/main/openapi/stable/apis/get_images.json)",
